  "text": "The procedure was a modified from [CITATION_1] and consisted of 2 parts; a 3-day habituation/training period and a 4-day testing period. From three days prior to the onset of training and onwards, mice were food restricted by allowing only 18 h of access to food per day (3 p.m. to 9 a.m.) to reduce body weight to approximately 85% of their free feeding weight.",
